vel0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13621/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13621/canvas/1/77f2e66f-40e1-4899-a7aa-5d8613b080a4","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T13:52:22.741Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Unlike Reynolds, Alma is shot with the Swiss expanses in the background. She is open and free. Reynolds, on the other hand, has a tree with fallen leaves behind him, reflecting his prickly nature and tormented mind. This background recalls both the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW66753722 BCX2\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-00124.html\"><u>marble</u></a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW66753722 BCX2\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-03300.html\"><u>aged mirror</u></a> with which he’s been previously connected.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13621/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:232.20779220779212,111.42857142857136,1462.5974025974028,814.2857142857144"}}}]}]}]}